       ----lloogg==_f_i_l_e_n_a_m_e
              Log status change updates and  actions  to  _f_i_l_e_n_a_m_e,  instead  of  the  default
              _/_v_a_r_/_l_o_g_/_d_p_k_g_._l_o_g.  If this option is given multiple times, the last filename is
              used. Log messages are of the form:

              YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS ssttaarrttuupp _t_y_p_e _c_o_m_m_a_n_d
                     For each dpkg invocation where _t_y_p_e is aarrcchhiivveess (with a _c_o_m_m_a_n_d of uunnppaacckk
                     or  iinnssttaallll)  or  ppaacckkaaggeess  (with  a _c_o_m_m_a_n_d of ccoonnffiigguurree, ttrriiggggeerrss--oonnllyy,
                     rreemmoovvee or ppuurrggee).

              YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS ssttaattuuss _s_t_a_t_e _p_k_g _i_n_s_t_a_l_l_e_d_-_v_e_r_s_i_o_n
                     For status change updates.

              YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS _a_c_t_i_o_n _p_k_g _i_n_s_t_a_l_l_e_d_-_v_e_r_s_i_o_n _a_v_a_i_l_a_b_l_e_-_v_e_r_s_i_o_n
                     For actions where _a_c_t_i_o_n is one of iinnssttaallll, uuppggrraaddee, ccoonnffiigguurree, ttrriiggpprroocc,
                     ddiissaappppeeaarr, rreemmoovvee or ppuurrggee.

              YYYY-MM-DD HH:MM:SS ccoonnffffiillee _f_i_l_e_n_a_m_e _d_e_c_i_s_i_o_n
                     For conffile changes where _d_e_c_i_s_i_o_n is either iinnssttaallll or kkeeeepp.

       ----nnoo--ppaaggeerr
